<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.3.5">
<l>veṉṟi tantōm māṉam vēṇṭōm tāṉa memakkāka</l>
<l>viṉṟu tammi ṉeṅkaḷ vāṇā ḷempe rumāṉtamarkāḷ</l>
<l>niṉṟu kāṇīr kaṇka ḷāra nīrem maikkollātē</l>
<l>kuṉṟu pōla vāṭu kiṉṟōm kuḻama ṇitūramē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>We conceded victory; we do not want glory.</l>
<l>Give us our full lives now as charity to us, oh, companions of our lord.</l>
<l>Without slaying us, stay and watch until your eyes fill;</l>
<l>Like mountains, we are dancing to the kuḻamaṇitūram.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
